description: Trev, a 19 year old college sophomore, is into surfing, camping, and partying.When he's not at the beach, he said you can probably find him with his friends either playing video games or drinking beer. He said he doesn't place much emphasis on school right now and that's because he doesn't want to miss out on the parties and fun. Well, sounds good to us, Trev... we like to party too. The night after Trev's video and photo shoot he took us out to a party that was one of the craziest we've been to in a while. Let's just say that the next day is still a blur.Catch Trev in his video debut as he shows us what he does in-between all the parties and girls.
title: Trev
